費新台幣1,000元。\r\n中　　華　　民　　國　　111 　年　　12　　月　　21　　日\r\n                                書記官　卓俊杰","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/CHDV/111%2c%e6%b3%95%2c11%2c20221221%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"CHDV,111,法,11,20221221,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"法","JNO":"11","JDATE":"20221221","JTITLE":"祭祀公業解散"}